question: The overall voltage of the battery is therefore the sum of ________ of the individual cells.

nodes.text: Currents are the sum of the overall voltage of the battery of the individual cells.
Resistances are the sum of the overall voltage of the battery of the individual cells.
Weights are the sum of the overall voltage of the battery of the individual cells.
Voltages are the sum of the overall voltage of the battery's individual cells.
